query: Difference between Mamba architecture and Transformers
Difference between Mamba architecture and Transformers
answer: Mamba architecture offers faster inference, longer context windows, and lower hardware requirements compared to Transformers, which rely on attention mechanisms. Mamba uses state-space models for better scalability and efficiency. Mamba may replace Transformers in specific applications requiring real-time processing.
